SpamFilter
==========

SpamFilter is a generic spam filter class, meant to act as a facade
for specific implementations that can be hooked in.

=== Installation

This depends on which filter you use.  See for instance README.sa for
the SpamAssassin plugin.

Example
=======

  sf = SpamFilter.new
  



